<div class="help-content-wrap"><h3 id="how-to-view-transactions-bet-history">How to view transactions &amp; bet history</h3>
<h4 id="how-to-view-my-transactions">How to view my transactions</h4>
<ol>
<li><p>Log into your account and click on &quot;Me&quot;.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Go to &quot;Balance&quot; option to see transaction details.</p>
<p> <img src="../../../../assets/wap-transaction-history-1-gh.png" alt=""></p>
</li>
<li><p>Select the desired transaction category from the drop-down column &quot;All Categories&quot; on the top-right corner. </p>
<p> <img src="../../../../assets/wap-transaction-history-2.png" alt=""></p>
</li>
</ol>
<h4 id="how-to-view-my-bets">How to view my bets</h4>
<ol>
<li>Log into your account and click on &quot;Me&quot;.</li>
<li>To see Sports bets, click on &quot;SPORTS BET HISTORY&quot; highlighted in green.</li>
</ol>
</div>